  <brief_title>Evaluating the Efficacy of Vardenafil in Subjects With Erectile Dysfunction (ED) Administered 12, 18 or 24 Hours Prior to Intercourse</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Crossover Study Evaluating the Efficacy and Safety of Vardenafil Versus Placebo Administered 12, 18 and 24 Hours Prior to Initiation of Sexual Intercourse in Subjects With ED</official_title>
